        <Parent_String>locomotives by method of propulsion [300228417], locomotives [300113388], rail guideway vehicles [300228410], guideway vehicles [300212494], land vehicles by form [300215717], land vehicles [300212968], vehicles (transportation) [300219258], Transportation Vehicles (hierarchy name) [300042929], Furnishings and Equipment (hierarchy name) [300264551], Objects Facet [300264092]</Parent_String>
